snippet.title: Road of the Dead 2 - Lost Guns (Flash Game)
snippet.description:
Another masterpiece by Evil Dog Production, SickDeathFiend Symphony of Spectre (SoS) and the rest of the voice actors. This is the sequel to the Road of the Dead 1 with the same time setting. This game is massive....I LOVE IT. Too much zombies and very chaotic, I'm not gonna lie haha. Most of the time I got chills when playing this game.

The music in this game is amazing, "Together in Hell".
